Add a list of R objects to an existing meta_study object.

add_dataset.Rd

Add a list of R objects to an existing meta_study object.

Usage

add_dataset(
  x,
  dataset_name,
  data_type = NULL,
  engine = arrow::write_parquet,
  engine_args = NULL,
  file_ext = NULL
)

Arguments

x

Named list of objects to create an arrow-compatible data set from.

dataset_name

Character scalar. Name of the database folder that should be created.

data_type, file_ext

Character scalar. Specify file suffix and file extension, respectively. (Default: NULL)

engine

function The function that will write out the content of x. (Default: arrow::write_parquet)

engine_args

list of other arguments to engine function argument. (Default: NULL)
